---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Caravan Upholstery" description="Caravan cushion and mattress specialists in Brisbane. Refresh your caravan interior with new upholstery. Custom sizes and shapes.">
  <div class="px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Caravans</h1>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <p class="text-stone-700 mb-4">
          Whether you're restoring a vintage van or updating your modern caravan, we can help refresh your interior with new cushions, mattresses, and seating that look great and travel well.
        </p>
        <p class="text-stone-700 mb-4">
          Caravan upholstery has unique requirements - it needs to be durable, easy to clean, and able to handle the bumps and vibrations of life on the road. We use fabrics specifically suited to caravan use.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Caravan Services</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-stone-700 mb-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Caravan cushions - all shapes and sizes</li>
          <li>Bi-fold and custom mattresses</li>
          <li>Dinette seating</li>
          <li>Day bed conversions</li>
          <li>Durable travel fabrics</li>
          <li>Easy-clean vinyl options</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Custom Sizes</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-700 mb-6">
          Caravans come in all shapes and sizes, and so do our cushions. We make everything to measure, ensuring a perfect fit for your specific van layout.
        </p>

        <img src="/images/013-Medium.jpg" alt="Caravan dinette seating" class="w-full rounded shadow" />
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-stone-100 p-4 rounded">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">What to Bring</h3>
          <ul class="text-stone-700 text-sm space-y-2">
            <li>• Your existing cushions (or measurements)</li>
            <li>• Photos of your caravan interior</li>
            <li>• Any fabric ideas or colour preferences</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-stone-700 text-sm mt-3">
            We'll help you choose fabrics that suit your style and stand up to life on the road.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-amber-50 p-4 rounded border border-amber-200">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Get a Quote</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-700 text-sm mb-3">
            Send us photos or bring in your cushions for a free, no-obligation quote.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-amber-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-amber-700 transition text-sm">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
